Package: epics-sscan-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libepics-sscan2.11.3 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         ${epics:Depends},
Conflicts: epics-synapps, epics-synapps-dev,
Description: Parametric scanning module
 Software for systematically moving positioners, triggering detectors,
 and acquiring and storing resulting data
 .
 This package contains headers and libraries needed at build time.

